  m_Name: Mata_8
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::PenyakitData
  tagBahagian: Mata
  namaPenyakit: Horner's Syndrome
  namaPenyakitEN: Horner's Syndrome
  tahapRisiko: Tahap 2
  tahapRisikoEN: Level 2
  gambar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f58f1c6496a0f624dbf7244915be3e86, type: 3}
  isGraphic: 0
  punca: Trauma fizikal, keracunan, jangkitan kuman, atau tumor.
  simptom: Anak mata menjadi kecil, kelopak mata layu/jatuh, dan kelopak mata ketiga
    tertonjol keluar.
  tindakan: Rujuk doktor haiwan.
  maklumatTambahan: Kebanyakannya bersifat idiopatik (punca sebenar tidak diketahui).
  puncaEN: Physical trauma, poisoning, bacterial infection, or tumor.
  simptomEN: The pupil becomes small, the eyelid droops/sags, and the third eyelid
    protrudes outward.
  tindakanEN: Refer to a veterinarian.
  maklumatTambahanEN: Mostly idiopathic (the exact cause is unknown).
